\cb3 Cross-Platform Availability: Currently envisioned likely as a mobile app (given the Apple emphasis), it could expand to a web application or have a desktop version. Many creators might want to use a computer for longer sessions. A web/desktop interface synchronized with the mobile app allows flexibility: record or upload on phone, fine-tune on a larger screen if needed. This could widen the user base (including those on other operating systems). Similarly, building an Android version would capture that market \'96 maintaining the same feature set so creators on any device can benefit.\cb1 \
