\cb3 Content Formats Beyond Video: While the focus is short video, horizontal growth could explore related content creation. For instance, generating image quotes or memes from the video content (if the video has a great quote, the app could with one click produce a nicely designed image for Instagram/Twitter). Or converting a video into a GIF for quick shares. Additionally, supporting audio clipping \'96 maybe extracting compelling podcast audio clips and turning them into audiograms or short waveform videos \'96 could attract podcasters. The core AI that identifies highlights could be repurposed for these formats with minimal adjustments.\cb1 \
