\cb3 Enhanced AI Models: Continuously improve the AI models for clip selection and editing. For instance, developing a more nuanced virality prediction model that not only considers general trends but is specialized per content category (analyzing what makes gaming videos go viral could be slightly different than cooking videos). Additionally, the AI could learn to detect emotional highs or punchlines by analyzing audience reaction (if source video has laughter or excitement, those are likely highlight moments). The better the AI gets at understanding content (both via computer vision and NLP for transcripts), the more accurate and valuable its clip suggestions will be. This might involve training on larger datasets of viral videos and continuously updating criteria as platform algorithms change.\cb1 \
