\cb3 Real-Time Editing and Recommendations: Imagine the app eventually offering real-time assistance \'96 e.g., if a user is recording a video (maybe a future feature where you can record a vlog or a tutorial in-app), the AI could give live tips like \'93Retake that line, it could be catchier\'94 or mark moments as you film that seem good. While ambitious, this would vertically integrate content creation during production, not just post. Even in post-production, the app could have an interactive editing suggestion mode where as the user manually edits, the AI pops up tips: \'93Clips like this often perform better under 30 seconds, consider trimming a bit\'94 or \'93Videos like this get more engagement with upbeat music \'96 press here to let me add one.\'94 This tight AI-human collaboration elevates the editing experience to a smart, assistant-driven workflow rather than purely manual.\cb1 \
